===Adverb===
'''generally'''

# [[popularly|Popularly]] or [[widely]].
#: ''It is '''generally''' known that the Earth is round.''
# As a rule; [[usually]].
#: ''I '''generally''' have a walk in the afternoon.''
# Without [[reference]] to [[specific]] [[detail]]s.
#: '''''Generally''' speaking...''

